      "name": "you've received from individual",
      "sender": "AD-FEDBNK",
      "receivedAt": "2025-03-19T09:00:00.000Z",
      "body": "John, you've received INR 10,509.09 in your Account XXXXXXXX1896. Woohoo! It was sent by TESTUSER on March 19, 2025. -Federal Bank",
