      "name": "you've received from masked 0000 sender becomes bank transfer",
      "sender": "AD-FEDBNK",
      "receivedAt": "2024-07-25T09:00:00.000Z",
      "body": "John, you've received INR 17,179.95 in your Account XXXXXXXX1896. Woohoo! It was sent by 0000 on July 25, 2024. -Federal Bank",
