      "sender": "AD-FEDBNK",
      "receivedAt": "2025-05-05T08:00:00.000Z",
      "body": "Hi, payment of INR 199.00 for Netflix via e-mandate ID: NX789XYZABC on Federal Bank Debit Card 3456 is processed successfully. To manage, visit: https://www.sihub.in/managesi/federal T&CA - Federal Bank",
